      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative solver residuals below 1e-6 for all load steps; energy convergence monitored throughout nonlinear solution.",
      "rationale": "All simulations converged with force residual norm < 1e-7. No load steps required bisection beyond two sub-increments. Energy balance monitored and consistent across all 13 model instances."
